{"tid":2350401,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"新手求教，GPU到底係咪有官方定價?","createTime":"2021-01-02T09:26:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T11:29:27.000Z","uid":33473,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"12e5859ebedf3002b31227d599184d69f300e1c2","tid":2350401,"uid":33473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"作為一個純新手，最近想砌女，今次想自己買硬件砌<br />\n<a href=\"http://當我選購不同的硬件的時候發現Price.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%95%B6%E6%88%91%E9%81%B8%E8%B3%BC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%99%82%E5%80%99%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BEPrice.com&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb00wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=2c3d20c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">當我選購不同的硬件的時候發現Price.com</a>上面有目前的市價<br />\n但我依然想有一個官方價格作為參考，想睇下到底市價同官方價格溢價左幾多<br />\n舉個例子，N卡RTX3080<br />\n我當佢的官方價格係USD 699，參考WIKI上面的價<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/NVIDIA_GeForce_30%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNVIDIA_GeForce_30%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%2588%2597&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb00wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=92ff2ff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/NVIDIA_GeForce_30%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97</a><br />\n而呢個價係指 Founders Edition 的售價?<br />\n咁如果我唔想要 Founders Edition  <br />\n我想要買<br />\nGIGABYTE, NV, RTX3080 VISION OC, 10GB GDDR6X<br />\n呢個型號GPU的廠有自己的散熱同包裝，咁到底呢個型號<br />\nGIGABYTE有無比出一個官方定價的呢?<br />\n定純粹係商業秘密，無官方的定價，睇市價?<br />\n又例如無市價呢一樣野，<br />\n咁上面的一堆OC 各廠自己的散熱等等係點決定各自係值幾多價，有無得估算?<br />\n例如OC的其實值得比多USD100，所以帶OC的係心目中可以當佢係用799USD咁做呢個溢價的計算?"},{"pid":"55904170f6b5b1288dc78836c2238de7b674e967","tid":2350401,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"非公板咪冇官方定價囉"},{"pid":"9a95e6eb4db056d4b0373302dbf86ee95a172a22","tid":2350401,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"55904170f6b5b1288dc78836c2238de7b674e967","tid":2350401,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply